{{vgname|北欧女神2 希尔梅莉亚|ja=ヴァルキリープロファイル2 シルメリア|en=Valkyrie Profile 2: Silmeria|cn=北欧女神2 希尔梅莉亚|hk=女神側身像2 希爾梅莉亞|tw=女神戰記2 希爾梅莉亞}}是女神戰記系列的第二部作品。遊戲由[[tri-Ace|tri-Ace]]開發，[[史克威爾艾尼克斯|史克威爾艾尼克斯]]發行。遊戲與2006年6月在日本發行，2006年9月在北美發行，2007年9月在澳洲和歐洲發行。

遊戲情節設定於前作《[[女神戰記|女神戰記]]》的數百年前，主角為轉生為人類公主阿麗莎的[[女武神|女戰神]]希爾梅莉亞<ref>{{cite web|author=Sam|title=《女神戰記 2》最新宣傳影片公布|url=http://gnn.gamer.com.tw/1/23651.html|publisher=巴哈姆特電玩資訊站|accessdate=2014-05-06|date=2006-05-26|archive-date=2014-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140506203420/http://gnn.gamer.com.tw/1/23651.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 開發 ==
{{expand section|time=2014-05-06T17:44:10+00:00}}
遊戲音樂由[[星海遊俠系列|星海遊俠系列]]的[[櫻庭統|櫻庭統]]作曲。遊戲有阿麗莎和希爾梅莉亞兩張原生專輯，每張專輯均分為兩碟，總計70首樂曲。

== 評價 ==

截至2008年11月30日，《女神戰記2 希爾梅莉亞》在日本售出40.1萬份<ref>{{cite web|title=GID 2451 - Valkyrie Profile 2: Silmeria|url=http://garaph.info/softwareindividual.php//gid/2451|publisher=garaph.info|accessdate=2012-06-21|archive-date=2014-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140506214212/http://garaph.info/softwareindividual.php//gid/2451|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據[[Media_Create|Media Create]]統計，遊戲以首周281,510套的銷量登上當周銷量榜首位<ref>{{Cite web | author=Klepek, Patrick | date=2006-06-30 | title=Valkyrie Profile Topples Mario in Japan | url=http://www.1up.com/do/newsStory?cId=3151890 | work=1UP.com | accessdate=2008-12-27 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060710003349/http://www.1up.com/do/newsStory?cId=3151890 | archivedate=2006-07-10 }}</ref>。截至2007年11月，遊戲在歐洲售出17萬套<ref>{{Cite web | title=FY2007 First-Half Period Results Briefing Session | url=http://www.square-enix.com/jp/ir/e/explanatory/download/20071119en_20.pdf#page6 | work=Square-Enix.com | accessdate=2008-12-27 | page=6 | archive-date=2012-04-24 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67AjkjbqF?url=http://www.square-enix.com/jp/ir/e/explanatory/download/20071119en_20.pdf#page6 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

遊戲獲得好評，在[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]和[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的匯總得分為85%和83/100<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamerankings.com/htmlpages2/931102.asp |title=Valkyrie Profile 2: Silmeria Reviews |accessdate=2014-05-06 |archive-date=2009-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090124053452/http://www.gamerankings.com/htmlpages2/931102.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/ps2/valkyrieprofile2silmeria?q=valkyrie%20profile%202 |title=Valkyrie Profile 2: Silmeria (ps2: 2006): Reviews |accessdate=2014-05-06 |archive-date=2009-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090725062538/http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/ps2/valkyrieprofile2silmeria?q=valkyrie%20profile%202 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。日本雜誌《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》為遊戲打出34/40<ref>NEW GAMES CROSS REVIEW: ヴァルキリープロファイル2 -シルメリア-. Weekly Famitsu. No.915. Pg.57. 30 June 2006.</ref><ref>{{Cite web | author=Fassino, Justin | date=2006-06-15 | title=GAF - News - Latest Famitsu review scores - Valkyrie Profile 2, Magical Vacation 2 | url=http://www.gamesarefun.com/news.php?newsid=5902 | work=GamesAreFun.com | accessdate=2008-12-24 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110612140315/http://www.gamesarefun.com/news.php?newsid=5902 | archivedate=2011-06-12 }}</ref>。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]打出8.0/10，因「看上去不錯」和「有趣而令人興奮」的戰鬥系統，稱遊戲為「清新且極具挑戰性的日式RPG實例之一」。他們稱讚遊戲的「深度和多樣性」，但認為技能和裝備介面「令人費解」，並稱其高難度「阻滯了劇情步調」<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/rpg/valkyrieprofilesilmeria/review.html | author = Greg Kasavin | date = 2006-09-29 | accessdate = 2008-04-20 | title = Valkyrie Profile 2: Silmeria Review | archive-date = 2007-10-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071021072116/http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/rpg/valkyrieprofilesilmeria/review.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。遊戲獲得[[IGN|IGN]] 2006年「最叫好不叫座」獎<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://bestof.ign.com/2006/ps2/36.html |title=IGN.com presents The Best of 2006 |accessdate=2014-05-06 |archive-date=2007-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070110000144/http://bestof.ign.com/2006/ps2/36.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並在2007年3月選入[[索尼電腦娛樂|索尼電腦娛樂]]的[[Ultimate_Hits|Ultimate Hits]]<ref>{{Cite web | title = Re-releases of Valkyrie Profile 2, Dragon Quest Gaiden Announced | url = http://www.rpgfan.com/news/2007/1103.html | date = 2007-03-27 | accessdate = 2008-04-20 | archive-date = 2008-07-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080715014829/http://www.rpgfan.com/news/2007/1103.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

